[I] A library that wraps a number of different spelling libraries and programs

[T] Enchant is a library (and command-line program) that wraps a number of
[T] different spelling libraries and programs with a consistent interface. By
[T] using Enchant, you can use a wide range of spelling libraries, including
[T] some specialised for particular languages.

